==Trivia==
*In the comics, Gilgamesh is one of the many identities assumed over the centuries by the Eternal known as the '''Forgotten One''', also known as the '''Hero''', who once joined the rank of the [[Avengers]]. He is based on the hero and demigod of the {{WPS|Gilgamesh|same name}}, the main protagonist of the {{WPS|Epic of Gilgamesh}}.
*In the closing credits, [[Don Lee (actor)|Don Lee]]'s credit is set alongside {{WPS|François Joseph Bosio}}'s {{WPS|Louvre}} statue of [[Hercules]] fighting a serpent. In the comics, Gilgamesh and Hercules are acquaintances and allies.

==Behind the Scenes==
*[[Xue Zhang]] was a stunt double for [[Don Lee (actor)|Don Lee]] in the role of Gilgamesh.

